<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> VVir ſenden cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Gunther </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l4">
<del rend="strikethrough">Müncʒmeiſter </del>
<expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> viſcher <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        dẏener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l5">mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden ʒureden von
                        Günther <expan>Muncʒmeiſt<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> . ſeiner güter vnd vveingarten wegen
                        cʒucʒeil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l7">vnd der <expan>Anlegu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> als die
                        gemaine von ʒygelanger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l8">auf <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_433_line_1577283455381_7426">ſein </ab></add>
                        weingarten . vnd güter geſlagen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l10">gelegt <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> vnd auch das ſein alſo darümb
                        be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l12">kümert vnd verpoten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd
                        doch <add><ab facs="#facs_433_line_1577283470522_7445">Sebolt
                                        <expan>pf<ex>incʒing</ex></expan> vnd
                                    <expan>pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>volk<ex>mer</ex></expan>
</ab><ab facs="#facs_433_r1l13">vnſ lieb </ab><ab facs="#facs_433_r1l14"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan>
</ab></add> ein aufſlag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l15">als ewr gnade wol waiſʒ
                            <expan>hıecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd
                            <expan>pfingſte<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l17">darümb <add><ab facs="#facs_433_r1l16">beredt
