<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l18"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> auch begert
                            <expan>cʒubleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Vnd bıten ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_433_r1l19"><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>dinſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ
